data.description: SELLER OFFERING $10K CREDIT FOR UPDATES WITH FULL PRICE OFFER! INVESTOR SPECIAL, PRICED ~$60K BELOW AREA COMPS! This 2 bed/1 bath ranch home could be perfect for a Fix & Flip, Buy & Hold, or owner occupant looking to invest some sweat equity. Home in need of cosmetic updates like flooring and paint. Large living room offers a fireplace and opens into the dining room. Dining room flows into the kitchen. Two bedrooms and one full bath with tub/shower combo. Out back there are 2 large decks overlooking the flat backyard. Huge detached 2 car garage and shed provide a ton of storage.
